	maps/is5_866.chs (1.3): - Fixed the SoftCRXlat translation method
	to work on the transport charset   instead of the local charset.
	This affects specifically the problem with   the cyrillic big en
	("H"). Please refer to the entry for the keyword   "SoftCRXlat" in
	the updated Msged manual.

