1999-01-06 Wednesday 23:50  tobi

	* ansi.c (1.9), config.c (1.12), dirute.c (1.3), dirute.h (1.3),
	init.c (1.8), msged.h (1.8), strextra.c (1.2), strextra.h (1.2),
	vsevops.c (1.2, msged-6_0_1-release, msged-6_0_0-release),
	doc/whatsnew.txt (1.17): Added the AdaptiveCase Feature. It allows
	MsgEd running on Unix to cope with mixed case file names in DOSish
	message bases or nodelist directories. See the Whatsnew.Txt file
	for more information.

