1998-12-06 Sunday 16:51  tobi

	* config.c (1.9), init.c (1.6), msged.h (1.6), readmail.c (1.13),
	doc/whatsnew.txt (1.15), doc/manual/msged.texi (1.16): Added the
	ReceiveAllNames and ReceiveAllAddresses features, which control
	when the Rvd flag is turned on for a mail. Also changed the default
	behaviour: Now the Rvd flag is turned on for any mail where the
	destination address is ANY of your AKAs and the destination name is
	ANY of your user names.

