	* makefile.ibo (1.1, msged-te-05-second-try, msged-te-05): Added
	makefile for IBM CSet

1998-07-25 Saturday 00:09  tobi

	* config.c (1.2): It is now possible to use more then one
	AreafileFlags keyword.

